You are:

passionate about what you do, you value excellence, learning and integrity
you enjoy a work environment that places emphasis on team work, collaboration and delivering business value
someone who is technically excellent and wants to grow further
proactive, detail-oriented and comfortable working in dynamic environments with fast paced deliveries and changing requirements
